## Recovery Procedures

### Quick Recovery
```bash
# Stop all services
./stop-development.sh

# Clear temporary data
rm -rf logs/* tmp/* .pids/*

# Reset environment
cp .env.example .env

# Restart services
./start-development.sh
```

### Full System Reset
```bash
# Backup important data
mkdir -p backup/$(date +%Y%m%d)
cp -r logs/ backup/$(date +%Y%m%d)/
cp .env backup/$(date +%Y%m%d)/

# Reset everything
npm run system:reset

# Rebuild from source
npm run build:clean
npm run build:all

# Restart with fresh configuration
./start-development.sh
```

### Data Recovery
```bash
# Database backup/restore
pg_dump database_name > backup.sql
psql database_name < backup.sql

# Configuration backup
tar -czf config-backup.tar.gz .env config/ logs/

# Recovery from backup
tar -xzf config-backup.tar.gz
```

